node_modules/
*.log
.pebbl/
.DS_Store

# Dogfood: this repo commits its OWN .pebbl/ store (decision history) so a fresh
# clone carries the reasoning. The .pebbl/ ignore above stays for consuming
# projects; this negation re-includes only THIS repo's root store. Survives
# `pebbl init` re-runs — init.js only appends `.pebbl/` when it's missing, and
# this line keeps the negation after it.
!/.pebbl/
